item.title: Bobby Hebb - Sunny - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song Sunny by Bobby Hebb from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A7, A♯maj7, Dm, Dm6, Dm7, Dmadd5, D♯9, Em7, Esus4, F9.

item.title: Billy Joel - Just The Way You Are - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song Just The Way You Are by Billy Joel from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A, A7, B, B7, Bm7, D, Dm, Dmaj7, E, Em, Esus4, F, F♯m, F♯m6, G.

item.title: Eric Clapton - Change The World - Ukulele Underground
item.description: Play along video for the song Change The World by Eric Clapton from the channel Ukulele Underground. Chords used in the song: A, A6, A7, B, Bm7, Cm7, C♯m7, E, E7, Esus4, F♯m, Gm, G♯, G♯m.
